ree variables... We need a practical approach.\n- For small number of free variables (say ≤ 20), enumerate.\n- For larger cases, we can use meet-in-the-middle on free variables.\n\nLet me implement this systematically."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":165,"cache_read_input_tokens":21121,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":165},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"59501f1b-ff80-4cf1-a763-d4e5cf2983c2","uuid":"31bcf4b1-1405-4884-8b86-df6b21dabcde"}
